# Pass 0134 Ledger: All-Video Author Theory Index

Date: 2026-07-01

## Objective

Index every locally recoverable YouTube/video source lead from the Telos
dogfood and demo receipts into an author, work, reference-expansion,
theory-chain, and experiment queue. This pass answers the request to look back
across sent videos from prior sessions by using durable repo/Gather receipts and
explicitly refusing to pretend that inaccessible private thread memory is a
complete corpus.

